title: Fairly OddParents - Breakin Da Rules - PC - al1o
description:
"Cosmo and Wanda have lost 'Da Rules' book and need to send Timmy Turner on a mission to get it back! Timmy will battle the evil Juandissimo, scare off the Yugo-Potaimian aliens and even dig deep into Vicky's nose - yuck! All to save his Fairy Godparents and earn his much needed good deed stamps for his Squirrelly Scout good deed badge!"

PC version of Breakin Da Rules, is different then other versions. Contains ISO without crack, just keep mounted to play. Requires Quicktime 6 (included) for videos.

Works for me on 64-bit Windows 7. I installed and ran it in Windows XP (sp2) compatibility mode. I'm not sure if that's necessary, but it's what I did =P
